{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"71e20ce2-c566-4179-883e-cdac1ebffec0","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, and tasks.md under specrunner/changes/bite-test-executor/ on branch change/bite-test-executor-a58cc81e. The plan covers: (D1) resolving isolated-worktree dependencies by symlinking the job worktree's node_modules (fail-closed if absent); (D2) an opt-in provider-neutral VerificationConfig.scopedTestCommand string + validation; (D3) per-file scoped execution under custom commands reusing the verification spawnCommand PATH/.bin executor, with the default and managed paths unchanged; (D4) never-throw + finally cleanup of worktree and symlink; (D5) no port-signature change (rides on existing config param); (D6) real-LocalRuntime integration + end-to-end tooth proofs. Tasks T-01..T-06 map to acceptance criteria T1-T6, and explicitly forbid editing .specrunner/config.json and src/core/port/runtime-strategy.ts.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-17T18:26:26.044Z","endedAt":"2026-07-17T18:35:29.152Z","commitOid":"14dacb01927e04396aba85ddd18d6548c479b3be"}
